Name: Kautic - The Bald Wizard
About the game: Kautic is an action platform game where villagers from a little Town have been petrified and now Kautic, the Bald Wizard, has the hard mission of saving them, but he will need to venture into a world controlled by evil creatures. Features 29 Different enemies Boss battles Choose your way through the game Different biomes Difficulty like in the classic plataform games Easter eggs Pixel art Full controller support
